## Notes

### Prisma Version Compatibility
- Original package.json specified Prisma 7.2.0
- Node 21.1.0 is not in the supported range for Prisma 7.x (requires 20.19, 22.12, or 24+)
- Downgraded to Prisma 5.22.0 which is compatible with Node 21.1.0
- Generator provider updated from "prisma-client" to "prisma-client-js"

### Database URL
- No actual database migration was performed (no DATABASE_URL in environment)
- Schema generation completed successfully with placeholder DATABASE_URL
- When actual DATABASE_URL is available, run: `npx prisma migrate dev --name add-review-system`

